videos.description: Jahaad Proctor sinks two consecutive 3-pointers, including a contested triple from the corner to beat the shot clock.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Proctor drains back-to-back 3s to power Purdue) 2020/2/5

videos.headline: Proctor drains back-to-back 3s to power Purdue

videos.description: Jahaad Proctor sees Aaron Wheeler on the fast break and sends a nice pass up ahead to him for a jam to continue Purdue's big lead.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Proctor's slick pass sets up Wheeler's jam) 2020/2/5

videos.headline: Proctor's slick pass sets up Wheeler's jam

videos.description: Tommy Luce drains two 3-pointers late in the second half, much to the bench and the crowd's delight in Purdue's blowout win vs. No. 17 Iowa.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Boilermaker crowd erupts as former walk-on drains pair of 3s) 2020/2/5
